text: Bayguzhino () is a rural locality (a village) in Verkhnegaleyevsky Selsoviet, Zilairsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 253 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 90 km from Zilair, 12 km from Verkhnegaleyevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zilairsky District
title: Bayguzhino
